content: Why don't cats play poker in the jungle? Too many cheetahs!
I told my computer I needed a break, now it’s sending me on vacation. Talk about a computer’s 'time off'!
I used to be a baker, but I couldn't make enough dough!
What do you call a dog magician? A labracadabrador!
I tried inventing a belt made out of watches. It was a waist of time!
I grilled a lot of steaks last weekend, but now I’m feeling a little burnt out.
Parallel lines have so much in common. It’s a shame they’ll never meet!
I went to a pub last night, but they didn't have any 'good' jokes. Just a lot of 'liquid humor'!
I burned my dinner last night... But on the bright side, I finally found my smoke detector's true calling!
I bought a banana, but I think it’s going bad. It’s feeling a bit peel-ish!
